review.body:
The McEliece ct-run looks ok on my test machine. Thanks for the update!

However, I didn't notice any BIKE errors. There also seem to be no issues registered in issues.json. I think [this file](https://github.com/open-quantum-safe/liboqs/blob/main/tests/constant_time/kem/issues/bike_has_no_timing_protections) could be removed since ct-fixes to BIKE were made in https://github.com/open-quantum-safe/liboqs/pull/1400.
